reviewText: I love getting to see any recorded live performance by SRV since we do not have him around to see live in person. Well done.
big fan of stevie loved his music dvd was great

SRV at his best absolutely proof of why he was and remains, to me, the greatest blues guitar player.  Need more DVD releases of this legend
